<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles/styles.css" type="text/css">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
            <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
        <title>Boarding</title>
        </head>

<%- include("partials/_header.ejs") %>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title"><h2>Boarding</h2></div>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>At our boarding facility, we offer a range of comprehensive packages to ensure your furry friend has a comfortable and enjoyable stay. Our dedicated staff provides personalized care and attention, ensuring your pet feels right at home. Choose from the following three boarding options:</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">1. Standard Boarding</div>
    <div class="card-content">
    <p class="train-title">Our Standard Boarding package offers a cozy and secure environment for your pet's stay. This package includes:</p>
    <ul id="training">
        <li>Spacious individual indoor kennel</li>
        <li>Regular feeding schedule with high-quality meals</li>
        <li>Daily exercise and playtime in our supervised outdoor play area</li>
        <li>Fresh water available at all times</li>
        <li>Daily health monitoring by our experienced staff</li>
        <li>Basic grooming and hygiene maintenance</li>
        <li>Regular updates and photos of your pet's activities</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="train-price">Daily Price: $30</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">2. Deluxe Boarding</div>
    <p class="train-title">Upgrade to our Deluxe Boarding package for extra comfort and additional perks. This package includes everything in the Standard Boarding package, plus:</p>
    <ul id="training">
        <li>Upgraded accommodations with a larger private suite</li>
        <li>Premium bedding and cozy blankets</li>
        <li>Enhance playtime activities and interactive toys</li>
        <li>Additional excercise sessions and longer outdoor playtime</li>
        <li>Extra treats and personalized attention</li>
        <li>Complimentary daily brushing and light grooming</li>
        <li>Access to our exclusive doggy daycare during the stay (subject to availability)</li>
        </ul>
    <p class="train-price">Daily Price: $50</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title">3. Luxury Suite Boarding</div>
    <p class="train-title">Indulge your pet in the ultimate luxury with our Luxury Suite Boarding package. This package includes all the features of the Deluxe Boarding package, along with:</p>
    <ul id="training">
        <li>Spacious private suite with comfortable bedding and a separate sleeping area</li>
        <li>Elevated pet cot for maximum relaxation</li>
        <li>Premium meals and gourmet treats</li>
        <li>Individual playtime sessions with our attentive staff</li>
        <li>Daily turndown service with soothing music and bedtime story</li>
        <li>Additional cuddle and snuggle time with staff members</li>
        <li>Complimentary bath and grooming session before departure</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="train-price">Daily Price: $75</p>
    </div>
    
    <p class="disclaimer">Please note that the prices mentioned above are for reference purposes only and may vary based on factors such as the size of the pet, requested additional services, and specific requirements of each boarding facility. We recommend contacting our facility directly for an accurate quote based on your pet's needs.</p>
    
    <p>Rest assured, our boarding facility is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities, adheres to strict cleanliness standards, and maintains a secure and welcoming environment for your pet's stay. Our trained and caring staff is dedicated to ensuring your pet's well-being and happiness throughout their boarding experience.</p>
    
    <p class="p-bold">Book a stay for your beloved pet today and enjoy peace of mind knowing they are in safe and loving hands!</p>
       </div>
   <%- include('partials/_footer.ejs') %>
 </body>
</html>       